{"tid":2100540,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我要由今日開始，成個熱門都係初選！","createTime":"2020-07-09T06:23:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T16:02:28.000Z","uid":230293,"like":20,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"62c8a688bc3f0c573c7f4f29f6f999f3b00bf5ec","tid":2100540,"uid":230293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T06:23:57.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">初選，並唔係真係初選。初選係香港最後一個真正既民主選舉。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n今次初選投票人數=香港擁有抗爭意志既人數=黃營既人數<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">如果今次初選一百萬人都冇，你點叫外國出手幫你啊？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">To想移民既人</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我諗你搞移民既手續，應該唔會因為你去投個靚票就搞唔切掛？<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">To想留守既人</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n今次初選之後，可能選贏既人會直接係9月被DQ。但係咁正正就係初選可以帶黎既其中一種效果，我地可以向世界證明中共係容不下任何一點反對既聲音。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">初選又唔洗手足送頭，又唔洗好似罷工咁驚畀人秋後算帳，仲要有靚畫面，你唔係唔投啊？</span></span>"},{"pid":"14150c191f547a52f566302b1ba80ac07e5f2140","tid":2100540,"uid":204872,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T06:26:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b53b57489f4f1a40b2878a3c6af9124e276b611f","tid":2100540,"uid":9028,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T06:27:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dbdc5c8dc6120cd5be456fe62f11406d43d0d034","tid":2100540,"uid":230293,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T06:27:50.000Z","msg":"推啊，初選啊屌你老母"},{"pid":"0fd411c63f3405dc526c5a386779c7900e933f99","tid":2100540,"uid":354476,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T06:28:27.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"67d08324ae9f5cfca4204f9bda9fe11c20c6f9ea","tid":2100540,"u